&lt;li&gt;Monitor competitive landscape and OEM market trends to identify opportunities for differentiation and early engagement in new product development cycles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Infinitum at OEM-focused industry events and technical forums to strengthen brand positioning and build strategic partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
