&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly execution-focused Revenue Operations Senior Manager to drive operational rigor, consistency, and accountability across our go-to-market organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is responsible for ensuring that our sales organization operates with clarity, discipline, and alignment. Translating commercial strategy into structured processes, clean pipeline management, and reliable execution. While informed by data, this role is less about deep analytics and more about driving behavior, enforcing process, and ensuring teams are operating effectively day-to-day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p3&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate is highly organized, proactive, and comfortable working directly with sales leadership to ensure alignment on priorities, pipeline health, and execution against commitments. This person thrives in ambiguity, pushes for clarity, and ensures things get done&lt;/p&gt;
